<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MediCloudX Labs - Cardiovascular Research Portal</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 90%;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .research-section {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #e74c3c;
        }

        .research-title {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .research-title::before {
            content: "ü´Ä";
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .research-content {
            color: #34495e;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .research-image {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .research-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .access-info {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #27ae60;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .access-title {
            color: #27ae60;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .credentials {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 10px 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
        }

        .metadata {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #95a5a6;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">MediCloudX Labs</div>
            <div class="subtitle">Advanced Cardiovascular Research Division</div>
        </div>

        <div class="research-section">
            <h2 class="research-title">Project MediCloud - Cardiovascular Analysis</h2>
            
            <div class="research-content">
                <p>Welcome to the MediCloudX Labs research portal. Our team is conducting groundbreaking research 
                in cardiovascular medicine using advanced cloud-based analytics and machine learning algorithms.</p>
                
                <p>This secure portal provides access to our latest research findings, including high-resolution 
                cardiac imaging data and preliminary analysis results from our ongoing clinical trials.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="research-image">
                <img src="https://${storage_account_name}.blob.core.windows.net/medicloud-research/close-up-doctor-holding-red-heart.jpg?${sas_token}" 
                     alt="Cardiovascular Research - Doctor with Heart Model" 
                     title="MediCloudX Cardiovascular Research">
                <div class="metadata">
                    Research Image ID: MCX-CVR-2024-001 | Classification: Internal Use
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="access-info">
                <div class="access-title">üîê Research Data Access</div>
                <p>Authorized researchers can access additional data files through our secure cloud storage system. 
                All research materials are stored in compliance with HIPAA and institutional review board guidelines.</p>
                
                <div class="credentials">
                    Storage Account: ${storage_account_name}<br>
                    Container: medicloud-research<br>
                    Access Method: SAS Token Authentication
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="warning">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice:</strong> This portal contains sensitive research data. 
                Access is logged and monitored. Unauthorized access or data exfiltration is strictly prohibited 
                and may result in legal action.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="research-section">
            <h3>üî¨ Available Research Files</h3>
            <ul style="margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Cardiac imaging datasets (DICOM format)</li>
                <li>Clinical trial preliminary results</li>
                <li>Research protocols and methodologies</li>
                <li>Authentication certificates for secure access</li>
                <li>Data analysis scripts and tools</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <strong>Azure AD Integration:</strong> This portal is integrated with Azure Active Directory 
                for enhanced security. Application ID: <code>${app_client_id}</code>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>MediCloudX Labs ¬© 2024 | Tenant ID: ${azure_tenant_id}</p>
            <p>For technical support, contact: support@medicloudx.labs</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hidden research metadata for internal use -->
    <!-- 
    Research Project: MediCloud Cardiovascular Analysis
    Principal Investigator: Dr. Sarah Chen
    IRB Protocol: MCX-2024-CVR-001
    Data Classification: Restricted
    Storage Location: Azure Blob Storage
    Container: medicloud-research
    SAS Token: ${sas_token}
    -->
</body>
</html>
